data.description: Pride of ownership is evident in this beautiful home! A chefs kitchen with beautiful stainless steel appliances, gas cooking, stunning showpiece vent, granite countertops and modern backsplash.  Floor to ceiling rock fireplace, and vaulted ceiling with wood beam creates a warm inviting living room. Floors are tile and wood laminate. Oversized primary suite is perfect for a king bed. NEISD schools, close to Randolph AFB, Ft. Sam AFB, restaurants and shopping!
